#-*- mode: gitignore -*-
#
# A reasonable default .gitignore for Android projects.
#
# This file is generated by the Android New Project Wizard.
#
# See https://raw.github.com/android/tools-base/master/templates/projects/NewProject/root/shared_root/gitignore
#
# For more details, see
#   * https://support.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/
#   * https://git-scm.com/docs/gitignore
#
# It's best to explicitly ignore all generated files and directories.
# A good default is to build the project and then use `git status` to see what
# files have been created, and then add them to this file.
#
# NOTE: Android Studio ignores this file, but it is used by the command-line
# 'git' tool.

